{"tid":1991872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國眾議院議長波洛西，表態支持前副總統拜登，代表民主黨競逐總統寶座。","createTime":"2020-04-27T18:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T00:15:08.000Z","uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d3f02fc15fe0a5992e445d4b9066b8acbf04b93","tid":1991872,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:45:41.000Z","msg":"波洛西發布短片，提到拜登過去在政府的經驗，包括協助通過奧巴馬醫保，證明他的領導才能，讚揚拜登帶來希望及勇氣，具備理性及韌性，有能力帶領國家，走出新型肺炎疫情的危機。<br />\n<br />\n波洛西是繼前總統奧巴馬及資深參議員桑德斯等人後，最新一名表態支持拜登的民主黨重量級人物。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523055-20200427.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523055-20200427.htm&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4WjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=0b500306\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523055-20200427.htm&h=6a2ce688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523055-20200427.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0493c0eeb34ed49b016d727cb897ebe79e7828b5","tid":1991872,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:58:37.000Z","msg":"預咗啦<br />\n<br />\n美國民主黨最後翻身機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b21123edc5b9eb8faffb8d35730199bc22abf4e","tid":1991872,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T23:16:18.000Z","msg":"大家同一個黨<br />\n可以唔支持咩"},{"pid":"5fe0b93fedc5214dade17744c4c99c9e3de48080","tid":1991872,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T23:27:34.000Z","msg":"香港媽媽佩洛西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0b666b911dc3914ae91a6084081fa20ea3c316","tid":1991872,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0493c0eeb34ed49b016d727cb897ebe79e7828b5","tid":1991872,"uid":70487,"like":0,"di